iwhen it starts, so after the deployment is complete and MongoDB has		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
istarted, we need to manually run the following command to create an		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iadministrator:		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i(Source:		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
hhttps://github.com/open5gs/open5gs/blob/main/docs/assets/webui/mongo-init.js	URL:https://github.com/open5gs/open5gs/blob/main/docs/assets/webui/mongo-init.js	{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
